11 "SECTION 3.3. Eligibility for Federal Decentralized Wastewater Funding. -- The
12 following entities are eligible to apply for and receive a loan or grant from funds appropriated in
13 this act to the Clean Water State Revolving Fund for decentralized wastewater treatment systems:
14 (1) A local government unit or a nonprofit water corporation, as defined in
15 G.S. 159G-20.
16 (2) A Community Development Finance Institution or a nonprofit organization
17 that provides financing assistance to homeowners to repair or replace
18 decentralized wastewater systems in North Carolina.
19 (3) A district health department established under Part 1 of Article 2 of Chapter
20 130A of the General Statutes.".
